&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are happy to facilitate socially distanced visits to the bases and the North Wales area with prior arrangement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Generous packages including re-location are offered to the best applicants and flexible working options including home working will be considered where possible.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
